 
<p>
The OLIGARCH act would <a href="https://www.commondreams.org/views/2022/07/19/joe-manchin-just-proved-why-we-need-oligarch-act">establish a graduated tax on wealth</a>.
<p>
I think it is a good idea, except for its use of median household
wealth as a measuring unit.  What if further impoverishment reduces
the median household wealth in the US to a negative number?

 